The Berkshire Funds - Berkshire Focus Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 24, 2017 12:51 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of The Berkshire Funds - Berkshire Focus Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
The Berkshire Funds - Berkshire Focus Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Berkshire Capital Holdings Inc. The fund invests in public equity markets of the United States. It invests in stocks of companies operating across the electronic technology sector including companies engaged in the development, production or distribution of products or services related to computer hardware and software, peripherals, mass storage devices, semiconductors, and telecommunications equipment. The fund invests in growth stocks of companies operating across all market capitalizations. It employs fundamental analysis with bottom-up stock picking approach by focusing on factors such ...
The Berkshire Funds - Berkshire Focus Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Berkshire Capital Holdings Inc. The fund invests in public equity markets of the United States. It invests in stocks of companies operating across the electronic technology sector including companies engaged in the development, production or distribution of products or services related to computer hardware and software, peripherals, mass storage devices, semiconductors, and telecommunications equipment. The fund invests in growth stocks of companies operating across all market capitalizations. It employs fundamental analysis with bottom-up stock picking approach by focusing on factors such as industry leader’s with dominant franchises and strong growth prospects to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the S&P 500 Index, Dow Jones Industrial Average, and the Nasdaq Composite Index. It was formerly known as the Berkshire Capital Investment Trust - Berkshire Capital Growth & Value Fund. The Berkshire Funds - Berkshire Focus Fund was formed on November 25, 1996 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


475 Milan DriveSuite 103San Jose, CA 95134-2453United StatesFounded in 1996



Phone: 408-526-0707

Fax: 408-944-0707

www.berkshirefunds.com







